import "../styles/Registration.css" import { useState } from "react"; const Registration = () => { const [regData, setRegData] = useState({ email: '', password: '', password_verify: '', name_organization: '', site_url: '', phone_1: '', phone_2: '', about: '', FIO: '', city: '', id_type_organization: 1, }) const [isOrganization, setIsOrganization] = useState(false); async function registration(e) { e.preventDefault() const email = regData.email const password = regData.password setRegData({email: '', password: ''}) } return (
setRegData({...regData, email: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, password: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, password_verify: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, site_url: e.target.value})} />
{isOrganization ?
setRegData({...regData, name_organization: e.target.value})} />
:
setRegData({...regData, FIO: e.target.value})} />
}
setRegData({...regData, phone_1: e.target.value})} />
setRegData({...regData, phone_2: e.target.value})} />
setIsOrganization(!isOrganization)} />
); }; export default Registration
